CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 17, 1970, pg. 1 reads: "BCC, Unions Agree - Left to right, Pat Navarro, Nate Smith, Angelo Carboni, and Judge David Olbum, examined the finalized draft of the new Pittsburgh Plan, designed to integrate Pittsburgh's construction industry."
TitMainTitle: Men, including Pasquale Navarro, Nate Smith, Angelo Carboni, and Judge David Olbum seated at conference table, with others behind them, for press conference to announce signing of the Pittsburgh Plan
